{
  "stem": "11671.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the restrictions started, you know, a couple of years before with curfew and the schools, not being able to go to the school that we went to.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our house was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So little things were happening, but not bad enough to fear for our lives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the, the Hungarian soldiers came and said, we need this house, because it was located across from the synagogue, and it was a location in the house, they had-- it had a cellar, and it had, in the same courtyard, we had a, a salami factory.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were evicted, and we were told to move out and took over our house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we moved like, just about four or five blocks away to another location.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in-- it, it was probably late 1943, because in April of '44, we were taken.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were-- we lived in Cluj, and, and by that time-- Romania became Hungary in 1940, so it was called Kolozsvar, the name of the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- the Hungarian soldiers knocked on our door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said to get ready in 20 minutes, that we will take you to work and to take with us clothing and food and broomsticks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they thought that we were going to work, and we were going to have to clean up, so whatever broomstick we had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we, we started, you know, running in every direction, trying to figure out what to take.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father-- we all started crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was in the middle of, of making bread that morning, and my father was in the middle of praying with his prayer shawl on him.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
